ady solution</span>
<o:p></o:p></p>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">Dear Team, it was lovely=
 meeting you last Friday!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">Producing the translatio=
nal process in the documents attached took me longer than expected. Sigh!&n=
bsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">I am requesting your fee=
dback on the attached document,
<i>Convert Research into a Business-Ready Solution</i>, focusing on the &qu=
ot;Research-to-Business Process Table&quot; and related &quot;Guide.&quot;&=
nbsp; R\Please return your completed feedback by 10 AM Friday August 15 - 1=
hr before we meet. We will discuss your feedback at the meeting.&nbsp;<o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">To make feedback consist=
ent and easy to consolidate, please use the attached Feedback Template&nbsp=
;(<i>Research to Business Feedback Template.docx</i>) to record your commen=
ts.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">Your feedback should cov=
er the following areas:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1">
<b>Steps in the Process Table</b><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Are the activities for each step clear, actionable, and logically sequenced=
?<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Are any steps redundant or missing?<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Are the outputs for each step sufficiently specific and measurable?<o:p></o=
:p></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"2" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1">
<b>AI Tools to Support Each Step</b><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"2" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Identify AI tools that could help execute each step efficiently (e.g., lite=
rature search, data synthesis, solution evaluation, presentation preparatio=
n).<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"2" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Where possible, name specific tools and describe how they would be applied.=
<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"3" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1">
<b>Additional Observations</b> <i>(if applicable)</i><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"3" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Any terminology that may be unclear to students or company stakeholders.<o:=
p></o:p></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"3" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Suggestions to improve alignment with a 13-week project timeline.<o:p></o:p=
></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ol start=3D"3" type=3D"1">
<ul type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1">
Opportunities to integrate real-world examples or templates for outputs.<o:=
p></o:p></li></ul>
</ol>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"color:black">Instructions:</span><=
/b><span style=3D"color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2">
Open the feedback template.<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2">
For each step listed in the first column, provide your comments in the seco=
nd column, list any AI tools in the third column, and add other notes in th=
e fourth column.<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"color:black;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-ma=
rgin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2">
Save the completed file with your name in the filename (e.g., <i>Feedback_T=
emplate_YourName.docx</i>).<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">Thank you for your contr=
ibutions toward refining this process so it=92s both academically rigorous =
and practically useful for our &quot;Up Our Game, Canada&quot; projects.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">See you Friday at 11 AM.=
&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">Best regards,<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
</div>
<div style=3D"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-bottom:12.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"color:black">Tony B.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
</div>
